WEBVTT

00:00:01.451 --> 00:00:02.601
Ljudsko poreklo.

00:00:03.225 --> 00:00:04.375
Ko smo mi?

00:00:04.741 --> 00:00:06.325
Odakle potičemo

00:00:06.349 --> 00:00:07.560
i kako da znamo?

00:00:08.391 --> 00:00:10.936
U mojoj struci, paleoantropologiji,

00:00:10.960 --> 00:00:12.732
istražujemo ljudsko poreklo -

00:00:12.756 --> 00:00:14.818
pitanja „ko“ i „gde“ -

00:00:14.843 --> 00:00:19.212
analizirajući fosile koji su stari
hiljade, čak i milione godina.

00:00:20.085 --> 00:00:25.681
Godine 2015, tim kolega i ja
imenovali smo novu vrstu roda Homo -

00:00:25.705 --> 00:00:27.305
našeg roda -

00:00:27.329 --> 00:00:28.479
Homo naledi.